  "text": "Soudani and Barhoumi [CITATION_1] used two deep learning classification models to recommend the most appropriate segmentation technique on ISIC-2017 dataset. Recently, Al-masni et al. [CITATION_2] proposed a fully resolution convolutional network (FrCN) to learn full resolution features of each pixel of dermoscopic skin lesion images for skin segmentation. They achieved Jaccard Index of 77.11% on ISIC-2017 testing set.",
